  m_text: '=============== Erase ==============

    To erase a an object like antipest,
    or to harvest palm tree you must type <color=#628141> erase_atxy</color> followed
    by number from 0 to 7 to refer to a grid position that occupied by object. If
    you typed this at the palm tree that has ripe and not occupied by pest you will
    get x 2 money.'
