    - target: {fileID: 5839410514789981349, guid: 8cc423796010e2447b8d54b60d4a7abd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: Pest
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6207713131432783878, guid: 8cc423796010e2447b8d54b60d4a7abd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '

        ----------------------------00000--------------------------

        ================
        Main ===============

        We are playing as Tarjo Prakoso, a literate
        sawit farmer that use automation to do his bussines. Instead of manually
        farm the land, he instead use drone that he controlled from he''s computer
        to farm. So instead of doing by hand Tarjo Prakoso type a command on a command
        line interface to manage his land.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
