    - target: {fileID: 8223627450847158084, guid: 8cc423796010e2447b8d54b60d4a7abd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '================ Plant ===============

        To plant a palm tree
        you must type <color=black> plant_atxy</color> followed by number from 0
        to 7 to refer to a grid position.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8413286638365591684, guid: 8cc423796010e2447b8d54b60d4a7abd, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "================ Pest ===============\nPest are spawning randomly at
        the given grid,  over time this object will spawn faster to struggle player
        a bit. \n\n\n\n\n\nIf a palm tree touched pest it will be useles as it wasn't
        gonna produce any money."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
